03/06/80  display_tsoapl_ws, dtw

Function: displays a saved workspace of IBM APL, as read into a Multics segment
by read_tsoapl_tape, listing the global names and their values.


Syntax:  dtw path {-control_arg}


Arguments:
path
   is the pathname of the workspace. The suffix sv.tsoapl is assumed.


Control argument:
-long, -lg
   lists the workspace global variables (digits, width, etc), as well
   as the names. The default is to list only the names.
